snippet.title: Drop Cooking // Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Play the Game ► https://store.steampowered.com/app/3115230/Drop_Cooking/

Drop Foods into the Pot and Cook the Dishes! In this exciting game, drop foods into the pot and create delicious dishes! When the necessary foods for a recipe come into contact, they attach together, and when all the required foods are combined, the dish is complete.

Developed by
Taka_Games
